    dc:description "Figure 1. Sclerotized plate on tergum IV of Epichostis spp. (A) E. wufengensis, sp. nov., (B) E. magnimacularis, sp. nov., (C) E. tympanias (Meyrick, 1908) (D) E. proximitympanias, sp. nov., (E) E. termitruncatula, sp. nov., (F) E. termiprotrusa, sp. nov., (G) E. wenxianica sp. nov., (H) E. hamatilis sp. nov., (I) E. jiangkouensis sp. nov., (J) E. setilata sp. nov., (K) E. deltata sp. nov., (L) E. subrotunda sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5217043/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5217046>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Adults of Epichostis spp. (A) E. wufengensis, sp. nov.; (B) E. magnimacularis, sp. nov.; (C) E. tympanias (Meyrick); (D) E. proximitympanias, sp. nov.; (E) E. termitruncatula, sp. nov.; (F) E. termiprotrusa, sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5217046/files/figure.png" ;
